  "text": "The results of this study also demonstrate a greater reduction of inflammation (evaluated by hsCRP values) in patients who underwent a VLCKD regimen compared to patients who followed a SHMD regimen. This finding confirms previously published data [CITATION_1] , in which VLCKD was associated with a reduction of inflammatory variables.",
